Unbelievable.

07:08.095 --> 07:10.063
I-I tried to get inside
a few times,

07:10.063 --> 07:14.034
but the goons
won't let me in.
I'll be right there.

07:14.034 --> 07:15.135
Brian...

07:15.135 --> 07:18.105
You all right?

07:18.105 --> 07:21.074
Good evening.

07:21.074 --> 07:23.110
Mikey, relax.

07:23.110 --> 07:26.046
Yeah, you, too, Clark.

07:26.046 --> 07:28.048
So you're Dutch's kid, huh?

07:28.048 --> 07:30.050
Yeah.
Well, I hope you got
more manners

07:30.050 --> 07:32.019
than this potty-mouthed priest
over here.

07:32.019 --> 07:34.988
Look, I came here to tell you
that Patrick Darling

07:34.988 --> 07:36.990
is gonna offer you
a plea bargain

07:36.990 --> 07:39.993
that you're gonna
find acceptable.
And why should we
believe you?

07:39.993 --> 07:42.029
Because it's the truth.

07:42.029 --> 07:44.097
I give you my word.

07:44.097 --> 07:46.099
Well, if you're anything like
your old man,

07:46.099 --> 07:49.102
that's good enough for me.

07:49.102 --> 07:52.072
Get him outta here, will you?

07:52.072 --> 07:54.074
Brian, let's go.

07:54.074 --> 07:58.078
