08:01.114 --> 08:03.050
Clark!

08:03.050 --> 08:05.118
Yeah, c--thank you.
That's really good.

08:05.118 --> 08:08.088
(Woman) Anytime.
I get lonely sometimes.

08:08.088 --> 08:10.057
Sue me.

08:10.057 --> 08:13.093
Anyway, Nick promised he could
get Patrick to play ball.

08:13.093 --> 08:15.996
Now he just needed
to deliver.

08:15.996 --> 08:19.066
How'd he plan on
doing that?

08:19.066 --> 08:22.035
Well, behind every Darling man
is a good woman.

08:22.035 --> 08:24.104
Sometimes... two.

08:24.104 --> 08:27.040
(Chuckles)
Care to elaborate?

08:27.040 --> 08:31.111
Patrick was having trouble
with his... girlfriend.

08:31.111 --> 08:33.046
Carmelita?
Yes.

08:33.046 --> 08:36.015
She'd kind of flown the Coop
on Patrick's election night.

08:36.015 --> 08:38.085
Now Nick figured if he could
track down Carmelita,

08:38.085 --> 08:41.020
then Patrick would be
much more agreeable

08:41.020 --> 08:44.057
on the whole Fantini mess.
Did it work?

08:44.057 --> 08:45.092
Like a charm.

08:45.092 --> 08:48.061
Okay, what the hell is
so important that you got...

08:48.061 --> 08:50.030
What happened to you?

08:50.030 --> 08:52.099
(Makes popping sound)
We have some news
about Carmelita.

08:52.099 --> 08:55.002
Do--do you know
where she is?

08:55.002 --> 08:57.104
Hey, relax.
Well, what do you know?

08:57.104 --> 09:00.107
I have a phone number
where she can be reached.
Let's have it.

09:00.107 --> 09:02.109
Well, pat, I'm not gonna
give it to you.

09:02.109 --> 09:05.078
I'll let you talk to her...
If you retract the subpoena.

09:05.078 --> 09:08.048
Oh, you're...
You're kidding, right?

09:08.048 --> 09:10.050
No, he's not kidding.
I'm dead serious, pat.

09:10.050 --> 09:12.052
If you want to talk
to Carmelita,

09:12.052 --> 09:14.054
you'll retract the subpoena,

09:14.054 --> 09:17.991
make the Fantini brothers
a deal they'll accept.

09:17.991 --> 09:20.060
Do not let this go to trial.

09:20.060 --> 09:22.129
You two have sunk
to a new low.

09:22.129 --> 09:25.098
You're using Carmelita
for your own wretched gains?

09:25.098 --> 09:28.035
I know. Isn't it great?

09:28.035 --> 09:29.036
(Scoffs)

09:29.036 --> 09:30.103
Fine, okay.

09:30.103 --> 09:32.105
All right.

09:32.105 --> 09:34.107
Here you go.

09:34.107 --> 09:36.043
What--what is this?

09:36.043 --> 09:39.046
Just a little statement
declaring your unwavering intent

09:39.046 --> 09:41.014
to quash the subpoena.

09:41.014 --> 09:43.016
I don't want you
changing your mind.

09:43.016 --> 09:45.018
What the hell
has happened to you?

09:45.018 --> 09:48.021
The Fantini brothers
took their sweetheart deal,

09:48.021 --> 09:50.057
the subpoena went away--

09:50.057 --> 09:52.125
case closed.

09:52.125 --> 09:57.064
Now you probably want to beat
that Thanksgiving traffic, so...

09:57.064 --> 10:00.067
You know, before I leave,
I wanted to mention,

10:00.067 --> 10:03.003
I keep hearing these rumors.
Rumors?

10:03.003 --> 10:06.039
About Ellen Darling's death
and your involvement

10:06.039 --> 10:08.041
in a potential cover-up.

10:08.041 --> 10:10.077
(Laughs) That's ridiculous.
Is it, Clark?

10:10.077 --> 10:13.046
You have no proof
of anything.

10:13.046 --> 10:16.049
No, not yet, but if you
don't start cooperating,

10:16.049 --> 10:18.085
I'll make damn sure
I find some.

