Next question--

10:46.079 --> 10:48.115
Karen.
That's not a question.

10:48.115 --> 10:50.083
Actually, you know, um,

10:50.083 --> 10:54.054
I'm a little parched myself.

10:55.122 --> 10:58.025
Why not?

10:58.025 --> 11:01.995
So my sources tell me
that Karen nearly broke off

11:01.995 --> 11:04.064
her engagement
to billionaire Simon elder.

11:04.064 --> 11:07.000
There were a few bumps
along the road,

11:07.000 --> 11:09.002
but everything
is just fine now.

11:09.002 --> 11:11.104
In fact,
the wedding's next week.

11:11.104 --> 11:14.074
So it is true Karen's
tempestuous relationship

11:14.074 --> 11:16.076
with old flame Nick George

11:16.076 --> 11:18.078
nearly wrecked everything
for Simon and Karen?

11:18.078 --> 11:20.080
I think
you're a little mixed up

11:20.080 --> 11:22.082
on your specifics there,
Kate.

11:22.082 --> 11:24.985
There was an ex
stirring up trouble,

11:24.985 --> 11:26.086
but it wasn't Nick George.

11:26.086 --> 11:29.022
Hey, baby,
I think it's really sexy

11:29.022 --> 11:31.058
that you're a dad...

11:31.058 --> 11:33.060
But do I have to meet
your son?

11:33.060 --> 11:36.129
(Laughs) Elon is a great kid.
You'll love him.

11:36.129 --> 11:40.033
Rise up slowly.

11:40.033 --> 11:41.101
Maybe I'll buy him
something.

11:41.101 --> 11:42.102
Yeah?

11:42.102 --> 11:44.037
Like hot wheels.

11:44.037 --> 11:47.107
And now move into Navasana,
boat pose.

11:47.107 --> 11:49.042
He's 16 years old.

11:49.042 --> 11:52.045
