a 16 year old boy

11:52.045 --> 11:56.016
what he really wants,
now can I?
Uh, no, you can't.

11:56.016 --> 11:59.019
Hey, did we pick a place
for lunch yet?

11:59.019 --> 12:02.022
Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah,
my place, 2:00 P. M.

12:02.022 --> 12:05.125
Ama is gonna cook for us.
Your ex-wife is joining us?

12:05.125 --> 12:07.127
Yeah.
Fun. That's so--
that's so fun.

12:07.127 --> 12:10.030
Yeah. I thought it'd be
a good idea for you two

12:10.030 --> 12:12.032
to get to know
each other better,

12:12.032 --> 12:14.034
you know, for Elon's sake
and all.

12:14.034 --> 12:15.102
Yeah, I totally agree.

12:15.102 --> 12:17.070
Well, as you can imagine,

12:17.070 --> 12:21.074
this whole ama thing
