12:26.079 --> 12:28.048
Princess ama of wherever.

12:28.048 --> 12:31.018
Have you registered
your concerns with Simon?

12:31.018 --> 12:33.020
No, no.
It would be too weird.

12:33.020 --> 12:35.055
We were just getting out of
the boat position

12:35.055 --> 12:38.025
when he told me and...
Yoga, mom.

12:38.025 --> 12:39.092
Oh, yeah. I knew that.

12:39.092 --> 12:42.095
He just doesn't realize how
creepy and possessive she gets

12:42.095 --> 12:44.031
