can overcome

12:46.033 --> 12:48.101
the emotional infidelities of
high-stakes corporate espionage,

12:48.101 --> 12:51.071
you can, you know,
talk this through.

12:51.071 --> 12:53.006
Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm.

12:53.006 --> 12:55.075
Just... just be delicate.

12:55.075 --> 12:57.077
So later that afternoon,

12:57.077 --> 13:00.013
Karen took
her mothers advice to heart

13:00.013 --> 13:02.082
and, uh, decided
to give Simon a call.
