13:02.082 --> 13:04.017
Hey there.

13:04.017 --> 13:07.020
So listen, um, I was
sort of thinking about lunch,

13:07.020 --> 13:08.088
and--and...

13:08.088 --> 13:11.058
I think I wanted it
just to be the three of us--

13:11.058 --> 13:13.060
you know, you, me and elon.

13:13.060 --> 13:15.062
